==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Anyhow
<hw>A"ny*how`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In any way or
manner whatever; at any rate; in any event.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Anyhow</qex>, it must be acknowledged to be not a simple
selforiginated error.</q> <rj><qau>J. H. Newman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Anyhow</qex>, the languages of the two nations were closely
allied.</q> <rj><qau>E. A. Freeman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anyone</ent>⟦br⟧
